intending ...h5-h4! This forces the White knight to go to f3.} (9... g6 {
Was played in the game, and Black was objectively fine, but I feel that
allowing for} 10. f3 Bg7 11. e4 {wasn't worth doing.}) 10. Nf3 Be7 {Now, we
