{[#] What is our key move here which stops White from seizing the one-sided
initiative?} 6... e5 $1 {Black doesn't mind sacrificing his extra pawn for the
sake of the rapid development with moves like ...Bf5! He is doing just great
here and we are analyzing this in more detail in the chapter on 2.c4 d4 3.e3
with 4.b4.} *

